''Björn Stenvers'' (* 25 Gicurasi [[1972]] muri [[Arnhem]]) ni (CEO) umuyobozi mukuru wa [[Eye Care Foundation]] akaba yarashinze ishuri ndangamurage.

== ubuzima ==
Mbere, yari umuyobozi wa Fonds de dotation des [[International Council of Museums]]. Kugeza mu 2016 yari umuyobozi wa Fondasiyo y'ingoro z'umurage wa Amsterdam, ari na we yashinze. Björn ni we wenyine mu bitabiriye gahunda ya perezida y’abaminisitiri ba [[Ishuri Rikuru ry’Ubukungu n’Umurimo wa Leta uyobowe na Perezida w’Uburusiya]] (RANEPA, [[Ihuriro rya Gaidar]]), [[Uburusiya]] aho yigisha. <ref>[https://msi.ranepa.ru/ru/o-fakul-tete Преподаватели Факультета/ Fakultätsprofessoren ]</ref><ref>[https://campus4youth.ru/about/news_item.php?ID=384263 Senior Lecturer RANEPA ]</ref> Muri 2014 Stenvers yashinze ishuri rya "[[Rostov Kremlin]] Academy", muri 2015 yashinze "Ishuri Ndangamurage rya Amsterdam" <ref>[http://www.Amsterdammusea.org ]</ref>, 2017 '' [[[Aruba]] Inzu Ndangamurage'', ''[[Altai]] Inzu Ndangamurage'' na ''Ishuri rya Zoo rya Moscou''<ref>[http://www.moscowzoo.academy/ www.moscowzoo.ru]</ref><ref>[http://www.moscowzoo.academy/ www.moscowzoo.ru ]</ref> yo guhugura abakozi ba muzehe. <ref>[https://mgimo.ru/about/amakuru/amakuru/bjern-stenvers/ master ] </ref> Afite imyanya yubuyobozi mpuzamahanga; Umuyobozi wa '' Kaminuza y'Abaturage ya Amsterdam '', umuyobozi wa [[Inzu Ndangamurage ya Diamond i Amsterdam]], Iserukiramuco ry’umucyo wa Amsterdam akaba n'umuyobozi w’umurage ndangamuco w’isi wa [[Igihome cya Brest]], [[Biyelorusiya]]. Björn Stenvers yashakanye numuririmbyi [[Tamara Hoekwater]]. Afite impamyabumenyi nyinshi mumateka yubuhanzi, kwamamaza no gutumanaho. Björn ni umwuzukuru wumukobwa umwe rukumbi wumuhimbyi wa Otirishiya [[Franz R. Friedl]].<ref>[https://kipdf.com/regionalinformation-rund-um-oberkappel_5ab8059e1723dd379cc4706e.html Oberkappler Zeitung - Regionalinformation rund um Oberkappel (Ausgabe September 2013) Seite 17hafi ya Oberkappel, Nzeri 2013, p. 17.]</ref>

